<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
     FEATURE DEEP DIVE
════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="pvh-lp-features" aria-label="Brook features">
  <div class="pvh-lp-features-inner">
    <div class="pvh-section-header" data-pvh-enter>
      <span class="pvh-tag">What makes Brook different</span>
      <h2 class="pvh-section-title" style="max-width:560px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">Every detail designed around how cats actually drink — and what keeps that water safe.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pvh-lp-features-list" data-pvh-enter>

      <div class="pvh-lp-feature">
        <div class="pvh-lp-feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2c0 6-8 10-8 14a8 8 0 0 0 16 0c0-4-8-8-8-14z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pvh-lp-feature-body">
          <h3>Food-safe ceramic</h3>
          <p>No plastic taste, no BPA, no off-gassing. Ceramic is the same material as the plates and mugs in your kitchen — completely inert, naturally odour-free. Cats have sensitive noses; the material they drink from matters more than most owners realise.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pvh-lp-feature">
        <div class="pvh-lp-feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="4" y1="6" x2="20" y2="6"/><line x1="7" y1="12" x2="17" y2="12"/><line x1="10" y1="18" x2="14" y2="18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pvh-lp-feature-body">
          <h3>Triple-stage filtration</h3>
          <p>Layer 1 catches fur and food debris. Layer 2 absorbs odours and chlorine with activated carbon. Layer 3 removes fine particles. The result: clean, fresh water that tastes nothing like tap water from a bowl — and cats can tell the difference.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pvh-lp-feature">
        <div class="pvh-lp-feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="11 5 6 9 2 9 2 15 6 15 11 19 11 5"/><line x1="23" y1="9" x2="17" y2="15"/><line x1="17" y1="9" x2="23" y2="15"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pvh-lp-feature-body">
          <h3>Whisper-quiet motor</h3>
          <p>Under 25 decibels — quieter than a household fridge. Shy cats won't bolt at startup. Light sleepers won't hear it from the next room. Brook simply runs, all day, without drawing any attention to itself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pvh-lp-feature">
        <div class="pvh-lp-feature-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"/><line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"/><line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"/><line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"/><line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pvh-lp-feature-body">
          <h3>UVC sterilisation</h3>
          <p>Available on UVC models. A built-in UV lamp eliminates 99.9% of waterborne bacteria — E. coli, Salmonella, and others that a carbon filter won't catch. Particularly useful for older cats, cats with sensitive stomachs, or anyone who wants complete peace of mind.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

