<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
     FAQ
════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="pvh-faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
  <div class="pvh-faq-inner">
    <div class="pvh-section-header" data-pvh-enter>
      <span class="pvh-tag">Common questions</span>
      <h2 class="pvh-section-title">Things pet parents ask before buying</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pvh-faq-grid" data-pvh-enter>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>Will my cat actually use it? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">Most cats approach Brook within the first few hours. Some take a day or two. We've never seen a cat completely ignore running water — their instinct is to investigate it. If yours is the exception, our 30-day refund covers you completely. No return needed.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>How loud is the pump? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">Under 25 decibels — quieter than a household fridge. Most owners forget it's running until they hear their cat drinking from it.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>How long does shipping take? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">EU orders typically arrive in 7–14 business days. You'll receive a tracking number by email once your order ships. If your order hasn't arrived within 20 business days, contact us and we'll sort it immediately.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>Is it dishwasher safe? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">Yes. The ceramic bowl and all removable parts disassemble and go on the top rack. Ceramic doesn't absorb odours or harbour bacteria the way plastic does, so cleaning is more thorough and less frequent.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>How often do I replace the filter? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">Once a month with regular use. The triple-stage filter lasts about 30 days before it saturates. We recommend marking the date on your calendar when you first set it up.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>What's in the box? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">Brook ceramic fountain bowl and base, silent circulation pump, 1× triple-stage filter cartridge, EU power adapter (or rechargeable battery unit, depending on model), and a setup guide. Everything you need, nothing you don't.</div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

